	dprr:hasNoteText "Named in a decree of Pergamum about 132, reported by Josephus (AJ 14.251). Syme, against Münzer (RE) and Marcus (in LCL), considers him a Roman senator (RS, MS-RP 1.285-286; see now Wiseman, NM 251, no. 317).\n" .
